<h2><b>Step 2: Plan Your Campaign Timeline</b></h2>
<span style="font-weight: 400;">Create a detailed timeline for your fundraising campaign. Determine the start and end dates, as well as key milestones along the way. This will help you stay organized and ensure that you have enough time to promote your campaign effectively.</span>
